text: Teublitz () is a town in Schwandorf, in Bavaria, Germany. It is on the river Naab, 12 km south of Schwandorf, and 23 km north of Regensburg. == Twin cities == * Baborów, Opole Voivodeship, Poland * Blovice, Plzeň Region, Czech Republic ==References== Category:Schwandorf (district)
title: Teublitz
